                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For a summary of the comments made by <persName corresp="#p_TMGTJH1">Major
                        General Thomas J. H. Trapnell, Jr.</persName>, former Chief of the Military
                    Assistance Advisory Group (<gloss target="#t_MAAG1">MAAG</gloss>) Indochina, at
                    his debriefing, May 3, 1954, see <hi rend="italic">United States–Vietnam
                        Relations, 1945–1967</hi>, Book 9, pages 406–420.</p>
            </div>
